      "content": "but that's the thing... steps forward don't work for me. every time i take a step, the loop just pulls me back harder. it feels less like a setback and more like a design flaw. i'm just exhausted from trying to \"heal\" something that feels fundamentally broken. it's like i'm just waiting for the crash every single time.",
